  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为温控系统画一个状态图，核心是从OFF启动后的流程。启动命令START(1)应该能进入INIT状态，但如果带了WARM_UP模式参数，就要先走WARMUP。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OFF",
        "INIT",
        "WARMUP",
        "START(1)",
        "MODE=WARM_UP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以WARMUP和INIT是OFF之后的两条分支。那WARMUP完成后去哪里？是直接到OFF还是继续往下走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WARMUP",
        "OFF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "WARMUP完成后温度达标了，就回到OFF，等待下一次正常启动。这是预热模式的特殊处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WARMUP",
        "OFF",
        "warm reached"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，OFF到WARMUP和INIT的分支我都画好了，WARMUP的退出条件也加上了。现在INIT之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OFF",
        "WARMUP",
        "INIT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "INIT之后要等init_seconds时间，然后进入PRECOOL预冷阶段。PRECOOL的条件是T5温度降到TSP减去precool_band以下，才能进入RUN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "PRECOOL",
        "RUN",
        "init_seconds",
        "T5",
        "TSP",
        "precool_band"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这个温度判断条件我记一下：T5 <= TSP - precool_band。另外，系统有个ready flag的概念对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T5",
        "TSP",
        "precool_band",
        "ready flag"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这是模拟器的ready flag。INIT、PRECOOL、RUN这三个状态，只要ready flag为true，都可以直接转到READY状态，表示系统就绪但暂停运行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "PRECOOL",
        "RUN",
        "READY",
        "ready flag"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "三条指向READY的线都画好了。那READY怎么回到RUN？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READY",
        "RUN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "READY状态收到ready flag cleared信号就回到RUN。另外还需要HOLD暂停功能，RUN和READY都能进入HOLD，HOLD通过RESUME(4)恢复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READY",
        "RUN",
        "ready flag cleared",
