      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，用any表示任意状态都能响应STOP(2)或OFF(5)回到OFF。但有个重要的安全机制我差点忘了——SAFE_SHUTDOWN。",
      "elements_involved": [
