    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SAFE_SHUTDOWN是一个安全状态，INIT、PRECOOL、RUN、READY、HOLD、WARMUP这六个状态遇到Safety事件都要转入这里。最后通过RESET(6)且ACK_ALARM确认后，才能回到OFF。",
